		<Row Tag="LOC_UNIT_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_NAME">
			<Text>Amtsbürgermeister</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_UNIT_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A Great Person with one charge. Can only be trained in a Capitol, and the specific Amtsbürgermeister received is random. Each Amtsbürgermeister can only be received once. Cost increases per Amtsbürgermeister trained.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_MINE_PRODUCTION_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Mines in this city recieve +1[icon:YIELD_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_FARM_FOOD_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>This Farm receives +1[icon:YIELD_FOOD] Production.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_ADJUST_GREAT_WORK_SLOTS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Gain 1 Relic. Kloster gains 1 Relic slot.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="LOC_AMTSBURGERMEISTER_GRANT_COMMANDER_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Activate on an Army Commander to grant 2 promotions.</Text>
		</Row>

